Core Automation Components
1.1 CI/CD Pipeline (Jenkins)
* Dev: Trigger on every commit → run unit tests, static code analysis
* QA: Trigger on merge to develop → run integration tests, deploy to QA
* Staging: Trigger on merge to release → run E2E tests, deploy to staging
* Pre-Prod: Trigger on approval → smoke testing, UAT
* Prod: Trigger on approval or tag → deploy with canary/blue-green strategy

1.2 Test Automation in each environment
* Unit Tests: Run in Dev
* Integration/Functional Tests: Run in QA
* E2E Tests / Regression: Run in Staging
* Performance & Load Tests: Run in Pre-Prod
* Sanity Tests: Run in Prod post-deplo
